snippet.title: Monster Hunter Rise: Sunbreak - Free Title Update 1
snippet.description:
A hunter's work is never done. New threats emerge and your investigations into the Anomaly take a step forward in free Title Update 1, available August 10. 

Monster Hunter Rise: Sunbreak is available now on Nintendo Switch and PC / Steam!
https://www.monsterhunter.com/rise-sunbreak/

Start your journey today in Monster Hunter Rise, available now!
Nintendo Switch: https://store.nintendo.com.hk/70010000029013
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1446780/MONSTER_HUNTER_RISE

#Sunbreak #MHRise #Capcom
